Effect: [TriggerTime:PLAY] [Target:(your Opponent's cards with 80 or more Base Power)] [Effect:POWER, Value:-20] [Duration:END_TURN] [Target:(the Merry Men, even if they're in your deck,)] [Effect:POWER, Value:+20] [Duration:PERMANENT]

Name: Coterel Gang
EffectDescription: When drawn, every time this card has been played this game, give your The Legend of Robin Hood cards +9 Power until played.
Effect: [TriggerTime:DRAW] every time this card has been played this game, [Target:(your The Legend of Robin Hood cards)] [Effect:POWER, Value:+9] [Duration:UNTIL_PLAYED]

Name: Little John
EffectDescription: When played, give all cards with a Base Energy of 3 or less -30 Power this turn. Repeat if played next to Robin Hood.
Effect: [TriggerTime:PLAY] [Target:(all cards with a Base Energy of 3 or less)] [Effect:POWER, Value:-30] [Duration:END_TURN] [Repeat:( if played next to Robin Hood)]

Name: Flower Moon
EffectDescription: When played, give your Plant Life cards +20 Power this turn & next.

Name: Strawberry Moon
EffectDescription: When played, your Curious Cuisine cards gain +20 Power this turn & next.
Effect: [TriggerTime:PLAY] your Curious Cuisine cards gain +20 Power [Duration:TIMER, Value:1]

Name: Humorism
EffectDescription: When drawn, give a random card in your hand +50 Power this turn. When played, give this card +20 Power permanently. When returned to your deck, reduce the Energy cost of your Opponent's remaining cards by 2 for 2 turns. While in your hand, at the start of each turn, give your cards +5 Power this turn.
Effect: [TriggerTime:DRAW] [Target:(a random card in your hand)] [Effect:POWER, Value:+50] [Duration:END_TURN] [TriggerTime:PLAY] [Target:THIS] [Effect:POWER, Value:+20] [Duration:PERMANENT] [TriggerTime:RETURN] [Effect:ENERGY, Value:-2] [Target:(your Opponent's remaining cards)] [Duration:TIMER, Values:(2)] [TriggerTime:START] [Target:(your cards)] [Effect:POWER, Value:+5] [Duration:END_TURN]

Name: The Geocentric Model
EffectDescription: When drawn, for each Solar System card in your deck, give the Earth card +8 Power.
Effect: [TriggerTime:DRAW] [Effect:FOR_EACH_TODO, Values:(Solar System card) ( )] [Target:(the Earth card)] [Effect:POWER, Value:+8]

Name: Lolcat
EffectDescription: When played, if your deck contains 9 or more Cute Cats, give them, wherever they are, +14 Power until played.
Effect: [TriggerTime:PLAY] [Condition:DECK_CONTAINS, Value:>=9, CountEach:[Who:SELF, Where:CARDS_IN_DECK, CompareTo:(Cute Cats)]] [Target:(them, wherever they are,)] [Effect:POWER, Value:+14] [Duration:UNTIL_PLAYED]

Name: One Red Paperclip
EffectDescription: When played, steal 2 Energy from your Opponent. When returned to your deck, give them +30 Power this turn.
Effect: [TriggerTime:PLAY] steal 2 Energy from your Opponent. [TriggerTime:RETURN] [Target:(them)] [Effect:POWER, Value:+30] [Duration:END_TURN]

Name: Doge
EffectDescription: When played, if your deck contains Shiba Inu, give your Dogs cards +19 Power until played.
Effect: [TriggerTime:PLAY] [Condition:DECK_CONTAINS, Who:SELF, Where:CARDS_IN_DECK, CompareTo:(Shiba Inu)] [Target:(your Dogs cards)] [Effect:POWER, Value:+19] [Duration:UNTIL_PLAYED]

Name: info.cern.ch
EffectDescription: When returned to your deck, if it is the first turn of the round, give your Web Surfers cards, wherever they are, +18 Power until played.
Effect: [TriggerTime:RETURN] [Condition:TURN_IN_ROUND, Value:1] [Target:(your Web Surfers cards, wherever they are,)] [Effect:POWER, Value:+18] [Duration:UNTIL_PLAYED]

Name: Walking the United Kingdom
EffectDescription: When drawn, if you are losing the round, give your Angela Maxwells Walking the World cards +15 Power this turn.
Effect: [TriggerTime:DRAW] [Condition:ROUND_STATE, Value:Loss] [Target:(your Angela Maxwells Walking the World cards)] [Effect:POWER, Value:+15] [Duration:END_TURN]

Name: Walking Vietnam

Effect: [TriggerTime:RETURN] [Condition:TURN_STATE, Value:(lost)] [Effect:ENERGY, Value:-1] [Target:(your Angela Maxwells Walking the World cards)] [Duration:UNTIL_PLAYED]

Name: Walking Turkey
EffectDescription: When drawn, if you have lost at least 1 round, give your Angela Maxwells Walking the World cards +15 Power this turn.
